bola (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * MITM HTTP/HTTPS proxy with resource graph building.
  * Cross-identity authorization testing engine.
  * Response comparison with confidence scoring.
  * JSON, Markdown, and terminal report generation.
  * HAR file import (Burp Suite / ZAP Proxy).
  * JWT/Cookie/Bearer/OAuth2 token auto-detection.
  * Smart path normalization and finding deduplication.

